{"type":"question","id":2407,"title":"如何看待GFW对steam社区的封锁进一步加强？","uid":902,"topics":[720,4961],"contents":"<b>补充图片：</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180828/1535465286396064.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180828/1535465286396064.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180828/1535465286396064.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n———以下为题主见解———<br>\n<br>\n如下图所示，本熊亲测通过修改hosts仍然连接不上steam社区。早在“steam中国将在天朝推出”这个消息放出之时，我就预测steam国际版离彻底被墙只是时间问题，只待steam中国正式上线。现在看来似乎初见端倪。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180828/1535465181292628.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180828/1535465181292628.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180828/1535465181292628.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n最后修正一下图片上的错误，不是以政府养人民，而是以人民养政府。","date":"2018-08-28","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}